                Commercial Real Estate            


Houston PE firm expands construction supply business with third acquisition




Jan 3, 2017, 12:56pm CST






Industries & Tags


                    Commercial Real Estate,                 


            Construction,              

            Venture capital             














Olivia Pulsinelli


Senior web editor
Houston Business Journal













